# Eliza's Library Manifest
- **xx.yy.zz** - Category.Subcategory.Entry

  - **3.2.zz** - World of Darkness (Chronicles / New World Editions)  
  - **3.5.zz** - Miscellaneous Games (small enough to fit on one entry each)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
